---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ImageCard from '../components/ImageCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="Exercises - Formula 188cm">
	<h1>Exercise Routines</h1>
	
	<h2>Sprinting Protocol</h2>
	<p>Sprinting can increase HGH production up to 7 times. Perform 7-8 sprints daily, giving maximum effort until fatigue.</p>
	<ImageCard 
		src="/images/sprinting.jpg" 
		alt="Person sprinting on a track"
		caption="High-intensity sprinting is crucial for HGH production" 
	/>

	<h2>Stretching Routine</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Morning cobra stretch (minimum 5 minutes)</li>
		<li>Regular stretching throughout the day</li>
		<li>Focus on spine and leg stretches</li>
	</ul>
	<ImageCard 
		src="/images/cobra-stretch.jpg" 
		alt="Person performing cobra stretch"
		caption="Proper form for the cobra stretch exercise" 
	/>

	<h2>Cycling Technique</h2>
	<p>Special cycling method for leg lengthening:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Use stationary bike with adjustable seat</li>
		<li>Raise seat by 1/4 inch increments</li>
		<li>Cycle for 15 minutes daily</li>
		<li>Focus on proper form and technique</li>
	</ul>
	<ImageCard 
		src="/images/cycling.jpg" 
		alt="Proper cycling posture on stationary bike"
		caption="Correct cycling position with raised seat" 
	/>

	<h2>Additional Activities</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Daily sunbathing (30 minutes)</li>
		<li>Walking with proper posture</li>
		<li>Swimming</li>
		<li>Light resistance training</li>
	</ul>
	<ImageCard 
		src="/images/sunbathing.jpg" 
		alt="Person sunbathing"
		caption="Daily sunlight exposure is essential for growth" 
	/>
</Layout>